      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This unit excels in power delivery, utilizing individual throttle bodies to reach its 8,400 RPM redline with surgical precision. The drivetrain is bolstered by a functional M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring maximum traction through corners. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including the critical replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing adjustable damping rates for both track and street. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping consistent with spirited use, the internal mechanical tolerances and subframe integrity remain excellent.",
