      "description": "This 2017 Audi Q7 Prestige has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for luxury SUV. The Orca Black Metallic exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, with only minor, unavoidable road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the rear wheel well. The interior is draped in Nougat Brown leather that remains supple; while there is slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin is free of odors, tears, or stains. Every piece of technology\u2014from the Virtual Cockpit display to the 19-speaker Bose 3D sound system\u2014functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Under the hood, the 3.0T V6 engine provides smooth, responsive power. This vehicle boasts a complete service history performed at Audi intervals, including a recent major service that saw the replacement of spark plugs, filters, and a comprehensive brake inspection. The Quattro all-wheel-drive system is paired with tires that show roughly 75% of their life remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next long-distance journey.",
